quran[45]{c,v,t}:
  36,60,"wyqwl allah lahum twbykhana wtdhkyrana: 'alam awskm ealaa alsnt rusuli 'an laa taebuduu alshaytan wala ttyewh? 'iinah lakum eaduun zahir aledawt"
  36,61,"wamrtkm bebadty whdy, febadty wtaety wmesyt alshaytan hi aldiyn alqwym almawsil lmrdaty wjnnaty"
  36,62,"wlqd adll alshaytan ean alhaqu minkum khlqana kthyrana, 'afama kan lakum eaql -ayha almshrkwn- yanhakum ean atbaeh?"
  36,63,hdhh jahanam alati kuntum tueadun biha fi aldunya ealaa kfrkm biallah wtkdhybkm rslh
  36,64,adkhlwha alyawm wqasu hrraha; bsbb kfrkm
  36,65,"alyawm natbae ealaa afwah almushrikin fala yntqwn, wtukllimna 'aydihim bima btsht bh, watashhad 'arjuluhum bima saeat 'iilayh fi aldnya, wksbt min alatham"
  36,66,"wlw nasha' latamasna ealaa 'aeyunuhum bi'ana nudhhb absarhm, kama khtmna ealaa afwahhm, fbadaru 'iilaa alsirat lyjwzwh, fkyf yatahaqaq lahum dhlk waqad tumist absarhm?"
  36,67,"wlw shina laghayarna khalaqahum waqednahm fi amaknhm, fala yastatieun 'an yamdu amamhm, wala yrjeu wra'hm"
  36,68,"wmn nutil eumruh hataa yhrm nueidh 'iilaa alhalat alty abtda minha halat daef aleaql wadief aljsd, 'afala yaeqilun ann man faeal mithl hdha bihim qadir ealaa bethhm?"
  36,69,"wma ellamna rasulina mhmdana alsher, wama yanbaghi lah 'an yakun shaerana, ma hdha aladhi ja' bih 'iilaa dhikr yatadhakar bih 'uwlu alalbab, waquran byin aldlalt ealaa alhaqi walbatl, wadihatan ahkamh whikamh wmwaezh; liyundhir man kan hy alqalb mstnyr albsyrt, wayuhiqu aleadhab ealaa alkafirin ballh; li'anahum qamat ealayhim bialquran hujat allah albalght"
  36,70,"wma ellamna rasulina mhmdana alsher, wama yanbaghi lah 'an yakun shaerana, ma hdha aladhi ja' bih 'iilaa dhikr yatadhakar bih 'uwlu alalbab, waquran byin aldlalt ealaa alhaqi walbatl, wadihatan ahkamh whikamh wmwaezh; liyundhir man kan hy alqalb mstnyr albsyrt, wayuhiqu aleadhab ealaa alkafirin ballh; li'anahum qamat ealayhim bialquran hujat allah albalght"
  36,71,"awlm yar alkhalq 'anaa khalaqna lajlhm aneamana dhllnaha lhm, fahum malikun amrha?"
  36,72,"wskhkharnaha lhm, faminha ma yarkabun fi alasfar, wayahmilun ealayha alathqal, waminha ma yaklwn"
  36,73,"wlhm fiha manafie 'ukhraa yntfewn bha, kalantfae baswafha wa'awbariha wa'asheariha athathana wlbasana, waghayr dhlk, wyshrbwn albanha, 'afala yashkurun allah aladhi 'aneam ealayhim bhdhh alnem, wykhlswn lah alebad?"
  36,74,waitakhadh almushrikun min dun allah alihatan yebdwnha; tmeana fi nsrha lahum w'inqadhhm min eadhab allh
  36,75,"la tastatie tilk alalihat nasr eabdyha wala 'anfusahum ynsrwn, walmshrkwn walhthm jmyeana muhdarun fi aledhab, mtbry baeduhum min bed"
  36,76,"fla yahzunk -ayha alrswl- kufruhum biallah wtkdhybhm lak wasthzawhm bk; 'iinaa naelam ma ykhfwn, wama yzhrwn, wsnjazyhm ealaa dhlk"
  36,77,"awlm yar al'iinsan almunkar llbeth aibtida'an khalaqah fystdl bih ealaa meadh, 'anaa khalaqnah min nutfat mrrat batwar hataa kabir, fa'iidha hu kthyr alkhisam wadih aljdal?"
  36,78,"wdrb lana almunkar llbeth mathalaan laa yanbaghi drbh, wahu qyas qudrat alkhaliq bqdrt almkhlwq, wanasi aibtida'an khlqh, qal: man yuhyi aleizam albalyt almtftt?"
  36,79,"ql lh: yuhyiha aladhi khalaqaha 'awal mrt, wahu bjmye khalaqah elym, la yakhfaa ealayh shy'"
  36,80,"aldhy 'akhraj lakum min alshajar al'akhdar alrtb narana mhrqt, fa'iidha 'antum min alshajar tuqidun alnar, fahu alqadir ealaa 'iikhraj aldd min aldd. wafi dhlk dalil ealaa whdanyt allah wkmal qdrth, wamin dhlk 'iikhraj almawtaa min qbwrhm ahya'"
  36,81,"awlys aladhi khalaq alsmwat wal'ard wama fihima biqadir ealaa 'an yakhluq mthlhm, fyeydhm kama bdahm? bla، 'iinah qadir ealaa dhlk, wahu alkhalaaq lajamie almkhlwqat, alealim bikuli ma khalaq wyakhluqu, la yakhfaa ealayh shy'"
  36,82,"'inma 'amrih subhanah wteala 'iidha 'arad shyyana 'an yaqul lh: \"kn\" fykwn, wamin dhlk al'imatt wal'ihya', walbeth walnshwr"
  36,83,"ftnzh allah taealaa wtqds ean aleajz walshrk, fahu almalk likuli shy', almtsrf fi shuuwn khalaqah bila mnaze 'aw mmane, waqad zaharat dalayil qdrth, wtmam nemth, wa'iilayh turjewn llhsab waljza'"
  37,1,"'uqsim allah taealaa bialmalayikat tasif fi ebadtha sfwfana mtrast, wbalmlaykt tzjr alsahab wtswqh bi'amr allh, wbalmlaykt tatlu dhikr allah wklamh teala. 'iina mebwdkm -ayha alnas- lawahid la sharik lh, fakhlsu lah alebadt waltae. wyqsm allah bima sha' min khlqh, 'amaa almkhlwq fala yajuz lah alqism 'iilaa ballh, falhlf bighayr allah shrk"
  37,2,"aqsm allah taealaa bialmalayikat tasif fi ebadtha sfwfana mtrast, wbalmlaykt tzjr alsahab wtswqh bi'amr allh, wbalmlaykt tatlu dhikr allah wklamh teala. 'iina mebwdkm -ayha alnas- lawahid la sharik lh, fakhlsu lah alebadt waltae. wyqsm allah bima sha' min khlqh, 'amaa almkhlwq fala yajuz lah alqism 'iilaa ballh, falhlf bighayr allah shrk"
  37,3,"aqsm allah taealaa bialmalayikat tasif fi ebadtha sfwfana mtrast, wbalmlaykt tzjr alsahab wtswqh bi'amr allh, wbalmlaykt tatlu dhikr allah wklamh teala. 'iina mebwdkm -ayha alnas- lawahid la sharik lh, fakhlsu lah alebadt waltae. wyqsm allah bima sha' min khlqh, 'amaa almkhlwq fala yajuz lah alqism 'iilaa ballh, falhlf bighayr allah shrk"
  37,4,"aqsm allah taealaa bialmalayikat tasif fi ebadtha sfwfana mtrast, wbalmlaykt tzjr alsahab wtswqh bi'amr allh, wbalmlaykt tatlu dhikr allah wklamh teala. 'iina mebwdkm -ayha alnas- lawahid la sharik lh, fakhlsu lah alebadt waltae. wyqsm allah bima sha' min khlqh, 'amaa almkhlwq fala yajuz lah alqism 'iilaa ballh, falhlf bighayr allah shrk"
  37,5,"hw khaliq alsmwat wal'ard wama bynhma, wmdbbir alshams fi mtaleha wmgharbha"
  37,6,'inna zynna alsama' aldunya bizinat hi alnjwm
  37,7,whfzna alsama' bialnujum min kuli shaytan mtmrrid eat rjym
  37,8,"la tastatie alshayatin 'ana tasil 'iilaa almala alaela, wahi alsmwat wman fiha min almlaykt, ftstme 'iilayhim 'iidha tklmu bima ywhyh allah taealaa min shreh wqdrh, wyurjamwn balshhb min kuli jht; trdana lahum ean alastmae, walahum fi aldaar alakhirat eadhab dayim mwje"
  37,9,"la tastatie alshayatin 'ana tasil 'iilaa almala alaela, wahi alsmwat wman fiha min almlaykt, ftstme 'iilayhim 'iidha tklmu bima ywhyh allah taealaa min shreh wqdrh, wyurjamwn balshhb min kuli jht; trdana lahum ean alastmae, walahum fi aldaar alakhirat eadhab dayim mwje"
  37,10,"'ila man aikhtataf min alshayatin alkhtft, wahi alkalimat yasmaeha min alsama' bsret, fylqyha 'iilaa aldhy thth, wylqyha alakhar 'iilaa aldhy thth, frbma 'adrakah alshhab almudi' qabl 'an ylqyha, warubama 'alqaha bqadar allah taealaa qabl 'an yatih alshhab, fyhrqh fayadhhab biha alakhar 'iilaa alkhnt, fykdhbwn maeaha miayat kdhbt"
  37,11,"fasal -ayha alrswl- mnkry albaeth 'ahum 'ashadu khlqana 'am man khalaqna min hadhih almkhlwqat? 'iinaa khalaqna 'abahum adam min tin lzj, yltsq baedah bbed"
  37,12,"bl ejbt -ayha alrswl- min tkdhybhm w'inkarhm albeth, waejb min 'inkarhm wa'ablagh 'anahum yastahziuwn bk, wayaskharun min qwlk"
  37,13,w'idha dhkkiru bima nasuh 'aw ghafalu eanh la yntfewn bhdha aldhikr wala ytdbbarwn
  37,14,w'idha ra'awa mejzt dallat ealaa nbwwatk yskhrwn minha wyejbwn
  37,15,"wqalu: ma hdha aldhy jit bih 'iilaa sihr zahir byin. 'a'iidha mitna wsirna trabana wezamana bialyt 'a'iinaa lamabeuthun min qbwrna ahya', 'aw yubeth abawuna aladhin mdu min qblna?"
  37,16,"wqalu: ma hdha aldhy jit bih 'iilaa sihr zahir byin. 'a'iidha mitna wsirna trabana wezamana bialyt 'a'iinaa lamabeuthun min qbwrna ahya', 'aw yubeth abawuna aladhin mdu min qblna?"
  37,17,"wqalu: ma hdha aldhy jit bih 'iilaa sihr zahir byin. 'a'iidha mitna wsirna trabana wezamana bialyt 'a'iinaa lamabeuthun min qbwrna ahya', 'aw yubeth abawuna aladhin mdu min qblna?"
  37,18,"ql lahum -ayha alrswl-: nem sawf tubethwn, wa'antum adhla' saghrwn"
  37,19,"f'inma hi nafkhat wahdt, fa'iidha hum qayimun min qbwrhm yanzurun ahwal yawm alqyamt"
  37,20,"wqalu: ya hlakna hdha yawm alhisab waljza'"
  37,21,"fyqal lhm: hdha yawm alqada' bayn alkhalq bialeadl aladhi kuntum tukadhibun bih fi aldunya wtnkrwnh"